    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "rebuilding feels like a joke. how do you rebuild when the person who was supposed to do the building is already gone? i've been thinking about what i said... about the person i was being dead. it's like i'm just a ghost haunting a life that doesn't belong to me anymore. wouldn't it just be quieter if i just let it happen? if i just stopped fighting?",
